headline: 3 Reasons We Love GE Aerospace (GE)
summary: GE Aerospace currently trades at $248.07 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 301% since June 2020, more than tripling the S&P 500’s 91.4% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 35.8% thanks to its solid quarterly results.
